Shop RHW is a Toronto-based studio with a focus on solid wood custom furniture hand crafted by Rundell Haynes-Wells. 
In addition to being a craftsman, he also offers custom design consultation and renderings.

Rundell combines years of experience problem solving, exploring, and innovating, and has been a maker of things all of his life. 
He’s a natural born collaborator and is generous with the information he shares with his clients in the hope that more knowledge and understanding of custom furniture will inspire sustained interest and appreciation.

Please give me a call - 647-453-0093

profile:
We currently live in a world of assembly line furniture creating mass ideas for a mass population. At The Windsor Workshop we are able to offer you an exclusive opportunity where rather than settling for what everyone else has, we can deliver on creating something unique and bespoke, just for you. There will be no compromising when it comes to working with The Windsor Workshop. Our team of highly-qualified furniture designers will be able to help you create that piece of furniture you've been dreaming about for years. We will walk you through each step of the process from the early blue print designing stages, to custom picking your piece of wood from the sawmill, to creating your own custom finish. We want your input because at the end of the day it is all about you and your imagination. Essentially, we offer you the comfort of having your ideas come to life. 
 
We are proud to be a part of this niche market where we are able to offer you modern styles with a blend of old world methods to ensure the highest possible quality of furniture. At The Windsor Workshop, we use age old cabinet making techniques that have been tried and tested for hundreds of years to protect against warping, cracking, or breakage. Our products will last a life time. That is why we are proud to offer a lifetime warranty on all our products. 
 
Regardless of your furniture need, we are able to accommodate you to give you precisely what you desire.

Casualife Outdoor Living provides premium outdoor furnishings with original accents and accessories to Toronto and it's surrounding areas.  With two newly renovated locations, our flagship store in Markham and our second store in Port Credit Mississauga.

As a family-run business, we pride ourselves in working exclusively with manufacturers whom share the same family run mentality. We believe in providing uncompromised quality, paired with exquisite design. Whatever your space – big or small, traditional or modern – we have created casualife to exceed these needs. Our professionally trained designers and sales staff are here to carefully guide you through your journey in finding what is best suited to your taste and space. The passion our team has for their craft is contagious – we will have you amazed at the endless possibilities.

Get ready to explore, to be inspired, to create & live beautifully. Welcome to casualife Outdoor Living.
